Title: Day 6: 10:00 P.M. - 11:00 P.M.
Plot: Wayne continues to risk his health as he takes a stand that will force cooperation from the Middle East.Jack realizes he won't be able to break Fayed, so he and Doyle concoct a scheme to force Fayed to lead them to the location of the remaining nukes. But Fayed's ally engages in trickery that places the plan in jeopardy.
GuestStars: Ajay Mehta, Said Faraj, Merik Tadros, Ismail Kanater
